Smart and rugged
column17:
this pair of high ankle sneakers from Diesel comes with a blue exterior and a raised ankle. \r\n

\r\n\tTaking pride in a sinful and hedonistic style statement
column18: Diesel brings to you a range of footwear that will make you want to indulge. Dark beauty has become all the rage
column19:

Footwear Care

Gently dust these sneakers with a soft-bristled shoe brush.
